Package: evalid
Type: Package
Title: Methodologies for Improving External Validity of Randomized Experiments
Version: 1.0.0
Author: Naoki Egami and Erin Hartman 
Maintainer: Naoki Egami <naoki.egami@columbia.edu>
Description: Provides three classes of estimators (`tpate`) for effec-generalization and a sign-generalization test (`pct`) to conduct sign-generalization. Details of the methods are explained in Egami and Hartman (2022+).
